        public double calculateRoughDistance​(WeightedPoint distanceTo)
        Calculates a rough estimation of distance by |this.x - other.x| + |this.y - other.y| / 1.42 side can be at most 1.414x bigger at sides being 45 degrees so we use 1.42 to keep estimated distance less or equal to actual distance.
        Parameters:

        Returns:
        a rough estimate of distance to distanceTo point
